strings:
<voice_0x01001C90><se_high>Princess Medea: Ah! I'm sorry, I'm a bit preoccupied.
I was thinking about Marta.
<voice_0x01001C91><se_high>Princess Medea: I had a grandmother when I was little.

<voice_0x01001C92><se_high>Princess Medea: She died a very lonely woman.
She was never able to marry her true love.
<voice_0x01001C93>Princess Medea: It's a little ironic, really, when you consider my current circumstances.
<voice_0x01001C94><se_high>Princess Medea: (Sigh.) Fate is such a mysterious thing...
<voice_0x01001C95><se_high>Princess Medea: I wonder if I'll really be able to go through with this marriage...
